{
  "stem": "5891.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the doors, the big gates-- there was those big brown doors-- closed, nobody out there, on the street.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all you hear is screaming going on, and trucks coming and going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you don't know if they're going to come stop in front of your place, or next door, across the other side, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Anyway, I remember the men were all nervous.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, listen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If they're going to come and get us, we are just going to-- if we just only take one or two with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we're not going to go willingly like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they had their little get together.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody was kind of upset, and just waiting for that gate to open.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Their boards, whatever they had, from those things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they were not going to just give it up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after a certain amount of time, then at the end, when it was finished-- [IMITATES WHISTLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They blow that whistle again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the [GERMAN] was [GERMAN] And of course, they opened up the door again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And kitty corner from us, there was a Russian, a Russian block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was Russian gypsies in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's what it was, Russian gypsies, had emptied their whole block.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And of course, you could hear the screaming on the way out there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were screaming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was four or five trucks going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Screaming as far as you could hear with your ears.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were taking them crematorium, to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't know it at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But then the doors were opened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there got to be talking around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They emptied that block, and they were all put to the chambers, gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
